Activity Summary: Type of compound activity based on both the CAR antagonist mode readout and the cell viability counter screen.
Antagonist Activity: Type of compound activity in the CAR antagonist mode screen.
Antagonist Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition of CAR.
Viability Activity: Type of compound activity in the cell viability counter screen.
Viability Potency (uM): The concentration of sample yielding half-maximal inhibition of cell viability.
